Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 
5. Cakkavattivagga 
43. Mārasutta 
“Mārasenappamaddanaṃ vo, bhikkhave, maggaṃ desessāmi; 
taṃ suṇātha. 
Katamo ca, bhikkhave, mārasenappamaddano maggo? 
Yadidaṃ—
satta bojjhaṅgā. 
Katame satta? 
Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—
ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, mārasenappamaddano maggo”ti. 
Tatiyaṃ. 
